text: Alibay Samadov (Əlibəy Səmədov, born in Respublika Dagestan) is a Russian born Azerbaijani male weightlifter, competing in the 105 kg category and representing Azerbaijan at international competitions. He participated at the 2004 Summer Olympics in the 94 kg event.
